{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But before you knew it, they were just beat-- the-- the brownshirts would beat up on them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And people started to mill around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of them would holler encouraging words.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were also some people that stood on the sidelines, shaking their heads in disbelief and would sometimes, when it happened again, would have-- sometimes mutter, well, this isn't right.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We know Hitler doesn't like the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he always said he's a man at law-- a man of law and order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just give it some time till he's more in the saddle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was just starting out in-- in his new regime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He will not allow that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so the police would never step in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this-- this appeared, happened more and more often.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- I remember a very vivid scene when I probably was-- I don't know exactly how old I was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe five, six, or seven years old when I was of the age that I was fully aware of the fact that I'm a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother and I walked down the streets somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these brown-shirted characters, a hoard-- a big hoard of those characters came down the street, marching, in marching formation, with a little band in front of them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And singing a constantly-repeating refrain to-- to a regular song.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that refrain would come up again and again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Until, finally, it even landed into my little child's ear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I would-- I will like-- I'll recite it in in exact translation, and hear, well, that constantly reappearing ditty.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it goes like, once the blood of the Jews squirts off our knives, everything will go twice as well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the little child that I was, blood of the Jews, that stuck in, and the knife.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
